name: PoorPleb
description: PoorPleb ($PP) is a zero utility memecoin on the Ethereum network. PoorPlebs will be able to claim a free airdrop, whales will get NOTHING. PoorPleb ($PP) is an experiment designed to enrich the many and exclude the few. If you are a small player in some of the most popular memecoins out there you may be eligible to free claim.
